sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as External Client
    participant Runtime as Caikit Runtime<br/>gRPC :8085 / HTTP :8080
    participant TextGen as TextGeneration<br/>(Local Module)
    participant TextGenTGIS as TextGenerationTGIS<br/>(Remote Module)
    participant TGIS as TGIS Server<br/>gRPC :8033
    participant Embed as EmbeddingModule<br/>(Local Module)
    participant PEFT as PeftPromptTuning<br/>(Training Module)
    participant HFModel as HuggingFace Model<br/>(In-Process)
    participant STModel as sentence-transformers<br/>(In-Process)
    participant HFHub as HuggingFace Hub<br/>HTTPS :443

    Note over Client,HFHub: Flow 1: Local Text Generation Inference

    Client->>Runtime: POST /v1/task/text-generation<br/>or gRPC TextGenerationTaskRequest<br/>Configurable TLS
    Runtime->>TextGen: Python call (in-process)
    TextGen->>HFModel: AutoModelForCausalLM.generate()<br/>PyTorch (GPU/CPU)
    HFModel-->>TextGen: Generated text
    TextGen-->>Runtime: GeneratedTextResult
    Runtime-->>Client: JSON/Protobuf Response

    Note over Client,HFHub: Flow 2: Remote TGIS Text Generation Inference

    Client->>Runtime: POST /v1/task/text-generation<br/>or gRPC TextGenerationTaskRequest<br/>Configurable TLS
    Runtime->>TextGenTGIS: Python call (in-process)<br/>(backend_type=TGIS selected)
    TextGenTGIS->>TGIS: gRPC GenerationRequest<br/>Optional TLS/mTLS<br/>Client certs (optional)
    TGIS-->>TextGenTGIS: GenerationResponse
    TextGenTGIS-->>Runtime: GeneratedTextResult
    Runtime-->>Client: JSON/Protobuf Response

    Note over Client,HFHub: Flow 3: Embedding / Reranking Inference

    Client->>Runtime: POST /v1/task/embedding<br/>or gRPC EmbeddingTaskRequest<br/>Configurable TLS
    Runtime->>Embed: Python call (in-process)
    Embed->>STModel: SentenceTransformer.encode()<br/>PyTorch (GPU/CPU)<br/>with truncation handling
    STModel-->>Embed: Embedding vectors
    Embed-->>Runtime: EmbeddingResult
    Runtime-->>Client: JSON/Protobuf Response

    Note over Client,HFHub: Flow 4: PEFT Prompt Tuning (Training)

    Client->>Runtime: Training request<br/>gRPC/HTTP<br/>Configurable TLS
    Runtime->>PEFT: PeftPromptTuning.train()<br/>Python call (in-process)
    PEFT->>HFModel: Load base model<br/>AutoModelForCausalLM
    opt allow_downloads=true
        HFModel->>HFHub: Download model<br/>HTTPS/443, TLS 1.2+<br/>API token (optional)
        HFHub-->>HFModel: Model artifacts
    end
    PEFT->>HFModel: Fine-tune with PEFT<br/>torch.distributed (multi-GPU)<br/>NCCL/Gloo backend
    HFModel-->>PEFT: Trained prompt vectors<br/>(encoder.pt, decoder.pt)
    PEFT-->>Runtime: Training complete
    Runtime-->>Client: Training result
